Title:  Format Notes using Markdown

Seq:    9

Level:  2 - Tip

Body: 

You can use the [Markdown syntax](https://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax) to format the body of your Notes. This consists of a few formatting conventions that are both easy to read, and easy to write. Look beneath the Help menu for access to a handy Markdown cheat sheet. 

